        <p class="section-description">
          Acne is a common skin condition caused by clogged pores, excess oil production, bacteria, and inflammation. Bengaluru's humid climate, pollution, and hard water can aggravate acne. Professional treatment addresses the root cause -- not just the symptoms -- for lasting results.
        </p>

