        <h2 class="section-title">Our Acne Treatment Options</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Customised treatment plans based on your acne type and severity</p>
        <div class="treatments-grid">
          <div class="treatment-card">
            <div class="treatment-icon">&#128300;</div>
            <h3>Medical Acne Therapy</h3>
            <p>Prescription-grade topical and oral medications tailored to your specific acne type and skin condition.</p>
