            <p>Deep cleansing and hydration treatment to clear pores, remove impurities, and soothe inflamed skin.</p>
            <div class="treatment-detail">Frequency: Monthly</div>
            <a href="/hydrafacial-bengaluru" class="treatment-link">Learn about HydraFacial</a>
          </div>
          <div class="treatment-card">
            <div class="treatment-icon">&#127793;</div>
            <h3>Acne Scar Treatment</h3>
            <p>Microneedling, derma fillers, and fractional laser to reduce acne scars and restore smooth skin texture.</p>
            <div class="treatment-detail">Sessions: 3-6</div>
          </div>
